* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
* B1700 MIL Test Program 5 — Loop with COUNT
* Tests: LIT, COUNT FA, SKIP WHEN, GO TO, loops
* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
*
* Loop 10 times, each iteration incrementing T by 1 (via SUM).
* After loop: T should be 10.
*

START       CLEAR X                       * X ← 0
            LIT 1 TO Y                    * Y ← 1 (increment) [clobbers T]
            LIT 10 TO FL                  * FL ← 10 (loop counter)
            CLEAR T                       * T ← 0 (must be after Y load)

.LOOP       MOVE T TO X                   * X ← T
            MOVE SUM TO T                 * T ← X + Y = T + 1
            COUNT FL DOWN BY 1            * decrement FL
            SKIP WHEN FL EQL 0 FALSE      * skip next if FL != 0
            GO TO .DONE
            GO TO .LOOP                   * loop back

.DONE       HALT                          * T should be 10
